{"tid":1942570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開始迫自己賭錢","createTime":"2020-03-25T06:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T07:15:49.000Z","uid":58316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"242a7ebe92a92903cd67f57944562e9f0b672ee0","tid":1942570,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"男人冇壞習慣<br />\n感覺上<br />\n會早死d<br />\n太clean太企理<br />\n好似反而易領野<br />\n反而d柒下柒下<br />\n古古惑惑個d男人<br />\n好多都撈得唔錯<br />\n頤養天年<br />\n得以善終<br />\n老實人<br />\n純過蒸餾水個d<br />\n反而早死<br />\n就由今日開始<br />\n有波賭波<br />\n有馬賭馬<br />\n疫情過後<br />\n過大海玩幾手<br />\n煙就應該唔食<br />\n酒就每週飲少少<br />\n汽酒梅酒<br />\n點都要飲返少少<br />\n打飛機唔好忍<br />\n唔縱慾就算"},{"pid":"16f8500929ff6534de95b52aa9f265d7a4e52704","tid":1942570,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失戀？</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1942cee7463cff736bf4b58394bb14648e06d84","tid":1942570,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"大麻入面嘅thc 可以幫倒你"},{"pid":"c493850ff366fe8c016b18016cfcb060adc62ca6","tid":1942570,"uid":353352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好賭錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19144667ffab1b3b86c0a18ae3f4d66cbfc2dbf","tid":1942570,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"食煙飲酒咩都得就係唔好賭錢"},{"pid":"a616e9efe265120e3f635202cd1a441652071824","tid":1942570,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"我細個嗰下有個鄰居老豆賭錢穿櫃桶底 會計師牌有被人釘埋樓又買賣埋<br />\n而家只可以租居屋住"},{"pid":"cc0275c8076a405f3c39f8420863a70697291a34","tid":1942570,"uid":353352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"我認為你只要搵到自己興趣<br />\n對事物有返啲個人執著，唔洗係咩壞習慣<br />\n都可以令自己無咁平凡......"},{"pid":"02d21b0bbaf0